ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely take this course! The material covered is such that students in almost any field of study will find it relevant and intriguing.
I would recommend this class to another student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Gave me better insight into how ethnographies are constructed. Will help me in conceptualizing how to talk about historical memory and its impact on society.
It exposed me to some of the literature and ideas relevant to my research.
